{
  "2201390": {
    "name": "Palladise Island：Legendary Space",
    "steam_appid": 2201390,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201390/extras/14e15f093db6a80dc2360967c1ccc534.avif?t=1762785328\" width=600 height=112 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>故事背景</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《帕拉小岛：传说时空》是一款轻松的角色扮演游戏，玩家在各种复古游戏里进行冒险，同时收集羁绊之力，带上新的同伴“唯灵”一起，踏上拯救世界的冒险旅途。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >异世界存在一种奇特的生物，称之为“唯灵”，从上古时代开始，人与唯灵就共同生活在异世界里，他们中最具有代表性的就是“唯灵训练师”。而在异世界的暗处，兴起的一股邪恶力量，异星人组织，他们为了统治异世界，企图打开连接现实世界的时空之门，破坏异世界与现实世界之间的平衡。正如传说中的寓言那样，关闭时空之门的关键就是——羁绊之力，只有打败异世界里那些强大的训练师首领，收集羁绊之力，才能拯救异世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201390/extras/67e6a0ccc9d5e6df5ca9bd97611970e6.avif?t=1762785328\" width=600 height=112 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>与你的同伴一起战斗！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >合理搭配队伍，进行最多4V4的战斗，属性相克是至关重要的一环，普通，草，水，火，电，冰，虫，地面，岩石，邪恶，格斗，飞行，大气，钢，超能，龙，毒，鬼，仙，暗，光，总共21种属性创造属于你的队伍！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201390/extras/2c7a29862fc72ccd3ca62c2b1a64fe21.poster.avif?t=1762785328\" width=426 height=246 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201390/extras/2c7a29862fc72ccd3ca62c2b1a64fe21.webm?t=1762785328\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201390/extras/2c7a29862fc72ccd3ca62c2b1a64fe21.mp4?t=1762785328\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>收集所有的图鉴，目标是成为PA大师！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过主线，支线等各种有趣的任务和战斗，捕捉世界各地的唯灵成为你的同伴，有着将近200只以上的原创唯灵等待塞满你的图鉴，满足你的收集欲望！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201390/extras/b8259cb489920bc637400962feb37d6b.poster.avif?t=1762785328\" width=426 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201390/extras/b8259cb489920bc637400962feb37d6b.webm?t=1762785328\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201390/extras/b8259cb489920bc637400962feb37d6b.mp4?t=1762785328\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>轻松诙谐的幽默剧情，挑战并收集首领们的羁绊之力！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >进入虚拟的电子游戏世界，里面的首领们拥有着羁绊之力，打败并收集他们的力量，开启时空之门拯救虚拟与现实世界，未知的挑战等待着你。当然，还有那传说中的唯灵！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201390/extras/e1f8018b5fc46ff8624fdba9df26b9a7.poster.avif?t=1762785328\" width=426 height=246 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201390/extras/e1f8018b5fc46ff8624fdba9df26b9a7.webm?t=1762785328\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201390/extras/e1f8018b5fc46ff8624fdba9df26b9a7.mp4?t=1762785328\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>注意事项</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >已知变异宠物有贴图错误的情况，在仓库界面将其放生即可，不影响游戏进程。 </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎加入玩家交流群：703313935，为您解决遇到的各种问题。</p></li></ul>",
